/Archives/
yolo12s.pt

# Re-include selective report assets across all strategies
!**/optimal_output/
!**/optimal_output/runs/
!**/optimal_output/runs/results.png
!**/optimal_output/runs/results.csv
!**/optimal_output/runs/BoxPR_curve.png
